&lt;p&gt;via &lt;a href=&#34;http://bustr.tumblr.com/post/15783965410/my-problem-with-listing-3-things-im-grateful-for&#34;&gt;Buster Benson&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At our house we have a nightly ritual of listing three things we&amp;rsquo;re grateful for. We&amp;rsquo;ve had this ritual for a couple of years at least. Carissa instituted it, possibly as a countermeasure to a general negativity by the male members of the family. I&amp;rsquo;m pleased to learn it has been contributing to our happiness.&lt;/p&gt;
